title: Totalamp and Winamp (latest)
description:
16 reasons why people  Totalamp:
- Complete tree structure support in playlists, previous and next folder buttons, two repeat modes
- Full CUE and subtracks support including fade effects
- Custom multiple emotions and attributes for advanced subjective tagging
- Intelligent bilingual lyrics display and integrated editor
- 2D and 3D playlist, quick access panel
- Music commander for playlists and tracks management, multiple views
- Simple good-night timer module
- Playlists generator based on your criteria, USB stick or auto-radio export
- Custom application commands
- Track artwork cover
- Music database management, search filtering and sorting
- Internet radio support
- Playlists coloring
- Main panel modes and effects
- Exciting fine-tuning parameters
